ҸВ¬в”ҳГјв”ҳГӨв”ҳГЁв”ҳГўГҸв”Ӯ',\n    description: 'Streaming entertainment',\n    descriptionAr: 'ГҸВҝГҸВҪ ГҸВ¬ГҸв–’в”ҳГјв”ҳГЁв”ҳГ§в”ҳГЁ',\n    icon: 'ВӯЖ’Г„Вј',\n    bannerColor: 'from-red-600 to-red-800',\n  },\n  spotify: {\n    name: 'Spotify',\n    nameAr: 'ГҸв”ӮГҸВҝв”ҳГӘГҸВ¬в”ҳГЁв”ҳГјГҸВәв”ҳГЁ',\n    description: 'Music streaming',\n    descriptionAr: 'ГҸВҝГҸВҪ ГҸВәв”ҳГӨв”ҳГ в”ҳГӘГҸв”Ӯв”ҳГЁв”ҳГ©в”ҳГ«',\n    icon: 'ВӯЖ’Г„ГҒ',\n    bannerColor: 'from-green-500 to-green-600',\n  },\n};\n\n// Mock products data - replace with database query\nconst getProducts = (platformSlug: string, sort: string = 'newest') => {\n  const allProducts = [\n    {\n      id: '1',\n      name: 'Elden Ring',\n      nameAr: 'ГҸГ‘в”ҳГӨГҸВ»в”ҳГҘ ГҸв–’в”ҳГЁв”ҳГҘГҸВј',\n      slug: 'elden-ring',\n      price: 59.99,\n      compareAtPrice: 69.99,\n      rating: 4.8,\n      ratingCount: 1250,\n      image: '/placeholder-game.jpg',\n      isNew: true,\n      pointsReward: 60,\n    },\n    {\n      id: '2',\n      name: 'Cyberpunk 2077',\n      nameAr: 'ГҸв”ӮГҸВәв”ҳГЁГҸВҝГҸв–’ГҸВҝГҸВәв”ҳГҘв”ҳГў 2077',\n      slug: 'cyberpunk-2077',\n      price: 49.99,\n      compareAtPrice: 59.99,\n      rating: 4.5,\n      ratingCount: 3400,\n      image: '/placeholder-game2.jpg',\n      pointsReward: 50,\n    },\n    {\n      id: '3',\n      name: 'Baldur\\'s Gate 3',\n      nameAr: 'ГҸВҝГҸВәв”ҳГӨГҸВ»в”ҳГӘГҸв–’ ГҸВјв”ҳГЁГҸВ¬ 3',\n      slug: 'baldurs-gate-3',\n      price: 59.99,\n      rating: 4.9,\n      ratingCount: 2100,\n      image: '/placeholder-game3.jpg',\n      isNew: true,\n      pointsReward: 60,\n    },\n    {\n      id: '4',\n      name: 'Red Dead Redemption 2',\n      nameAr: 'ГҸв–’в”ҳГЁГҸВ» ГҸВ»в”ҳГЁГҸВ» ГҸв–’в”ҳГЁГҸВ»в”ҳГ ГҸВҝГҸв”Өв”ҳГҘ 2',\n      slug: 'rdr2',\n      price: 39.99,\n      compareAtPrice: 59.99,\n      rating: 4.9,\n      ratingCount: 5600,\n      image: '/placeholder-game4.jpg',\n      pointsReward: 40,\n    },\n    {\n      id: '5',\n      name: 'God of War',\n      nameAr: 'ГҸВјв”ҳГӘГҸВ» ГҸГәв”ҳГӘв”ҳГј в”ҳГӘв”ҳГӘГҸв–’',\n      slug: 'god-of-war',\n      price: 44.99,\n      compareAtPrice: 49.99,\n      rating: 4.8,\n      ratingCount: 1800,\n      image: '/placeholder-game5.jpg',\n      pointsReward: 45,\n    },\n    {\n      id: '6',\n      name: 'Horizon Zero Dawn',\n      nameAr: 'в”ҳГ§в”ҳГӘГҸв–’ГҸВәв”ҳГЁГҸв–“в”ҳГӘв”ҳГҘ ГҸв–“в”ҳГЁГҸв–’в”ҳГӘ ГҸВ»ГҸВәв”ҳГӘв”ҳГҘ',\n      slug: 'horizon-zero-dawn',\n      price: 34.99,\n      rating: 4.6,\n      ratingCount: 980,\n      image: '/placeholder-game6.jpg',\n      pointsReward: 35,\n    },\n  ];\n\n  // Apply sorting\n  let sorted = [...allProducts];\n  switch (sort) {\n    case 'price_low':\n      sorted.sort((a, b) => a.price - b.price);\n      break;\n    case 'price_high':\n      sorted.sort((a, b) => b.price - a.price);\n      break;\n    case 'rating':\n      sorted.sort((a, b) => b.rating - a.rating);\n      break;\n    case 'newest':\n    default:\n      sorted.sort((a, b) => (b.isNew ? 1 : 0) - (a.isNew ? 1 : 0));\n      break;\n  }\n\n  return sorted;\n};\n\nexport async function generateMetadata({ params }: PlatformPageProps): Promise<Metadata> {\n  const { slug } = await params;\n  const platform = PLATFORMS[slug];\n\n  if (!platform) {\n    return {\n      title: 'Platform Not Found',\n    };\n  }\n\n  return {\n    title: `${platform.name} - Fulmen Empire`,\n    description: platform.description,\n  };\n};\n\nexport default async function PlatformPage({ params, searchParams }: PlatformPageProps) {\n  const { locale, slug } = await params;\n  const search = await searchParams;\n  const sort = (search.sort as string) || 'newest';\n\n  const platform = PLATFORMS[slug];\n  if (!platform) {\n    notFound();\n  }\n\n  const products = getProducts(slug, sort);\n  const isRTL = locale === 'ar';\n\n  const SORT_OPTIONS = [\n    { value: 'newest', label: 'Newest', labelAr: 'ГҸВәв”ҳГӨГҸГәГҸВЎГҸВ»ГҸВҪ' },\n    { value: 'price_low', label: 'Price: Low to High', labelAr: 'ГҸВәв”ҳГӨГҸв”ӮГҸв•ЈГҸв–’: в”ҳГ в”ҳГҘ ГҸВәв”ҳГӨГҸГәв”ҳГ©в”ҳГӨ в”ҳГӨв”ҳГӨГҸГәГҸв•Јв”ҳГӨв”ҳГ«' },\n    { value: 'price_high', label: 'Price: High to Low', labelAr: 'ГҸВәв”ҳГӨГҸв”ӮГҸв•ЈГҸв–’: в”ҳГ в”ҳГҘ ГҸВәв”ҳГӨГҸГәГҸв•Јв”ҳГӨв”ҳГ« в”ҳГӨв”ҳГӨГҸГәв”ҳГ©в”ҳГӨ' },\n    { value: 'rating', label: 'Top Rated', labelAr: 'ГҸВәв”ҳГӨГҸГәГҸв•Јв”ҳГӨв”ҳГ« ГҸВ¬в”ҳГ©в”ҳГЁв”ҳГЁв”ҳГ ГҸВәв”ҳГҜ' },\n  ];\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"min-h-screen\">\n      {/* Platform Banner */}\n      <section className={cn('bg-gradient-to-br py-16', platform.bannerColor)}>\n        <div className=\"container mx-auto px-4\">\n          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-6\">\n            <div className=\"w-24 h-24 rounded-2xl bg-white/20 backdrop-blur flex items-center justify-center text-6xl\">\n              {platform.icon}\n            </div>\n            <div>\n              <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\">\n                <h1 className=\"text-4xl font-bold\">\n                  {isRTL ? platform.nameAr : platform.name}\n                </h1>\n                <Badge variant=\"featured\">{products.length}+ Products</Badge>\n              </div>\n              <p className=\"text-white/80 text-lg\">\n                {isRTL ? platform.descriptionAr : platform.description}\n              </p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      {/* Filters and Sort */}\n      <section className=\"sticky top-0 z-30 bg-background-light border-b border-border/50 py-4\">\n        <div className=\"container mx-auto px-4\">\n          <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n              <Button variant=\"outline\" size=\"sm\">\n                <SlidersHorizontal className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n                {locale === 'ar' ? 'в”ҳГјв”ҳГӨГҸВәГҸВ¬ГҸв–’' : 'Filters'}\n              </Button>\n              <div className=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-text-muted\">\n                <span>{products.length}</span>\n                <span>{locale === 'ar' ? 'в”ҳГ в”ҳГҘГҸВ¬ГҸВј' : 'products'}</span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n              <span className=\"text-sm text-text-muted hidden sm:inline\">\n                {locale === 'ar' ? 'ГҸВ¬ГҸв–’ГҸВ¬в”ҳГЁГҸВҝ ГҸВЎГҸв”ӮГҸВҝ:' : 'Sort by:'}\n              </span>\n              <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1\">\n                {SORT_OPTIONS.map((option) => (\n                  <Link\n                    key={option.value}\n                    href={`/${locale}/platforms/${slug}?sort=${option.value}`}\n                  >\n                    <Button\n                      variant={sort === option.value ? 'primary' : 'ghost'}\n                      size=\"sm\"\n                    >\n                      {isRTL ? option.labelAr : option.label}\n                    </Button>\n                  </Link>\n                ))}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      {/* Products Grid */}\n      <section className=\"py-12\">\n        <div className=\"container mx-auto px-4\">\n          {products.length === 0 ? (\n            <div className=\"text-center py-16\">\n              <p className=\"text-text-muted text-lg\">\n                {locale === 'ar' ? 'в”ҳГӨГҸВә ГҸВ¬в”ҳГӘГҸВјГҸВ» в”ҳГ в”ҳГҘГҸВ¬ГҸВјГҸВәГҸВ¬ в”ҳГ ГҸВ¬ГҸВәГҸВЎГҸВ®' : 'No products available'}\n              </p>\n            </div>\n          ) : (\n            <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-6\">\n              {products.map((product) => (\n                <ProductCard\n                  key={product.id}\n                  product={product}\n                  platformSlug={slug}\n                  locale={locale}\n                />\n              ))}\n            </div>\n          )}\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n\nfunction ProductCard({\n  product,\n  platformSlug,\n  locale,\n}: {\n  product: ReturnType<typeof getProducts>[number];\n  platformSlug: string;\n  locale: string;\n}) {\n  const isRTL = locale === 'ar';\n\n  return (\n    <Link href={`/${locale}/products/${product.slug}`}>\n      <Card className=\"group h-full overflow-hidden\">\n        <CardContent className=\"p-0\">\n          {/* Image */}\n          <div className=\"relative aspect-square bg-background-lighter overflow-hidden\">\n            <div className=\"absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-6xl\">\n              ВӯЖ’Г„В«\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Badges */}\n            <div className=\"absolute top-3 left-3 flex flex-col gap-2\">\n              {product.isNew && (\n                <Badge variant=\"new\" size=\"sm\">\n                  {locale === 'ar' ? 'ГҸВјГҸВ»в”ҳГЁГҸВ»' : 'NEW'}\n                </Badge>\n              )}\n              {product.compareAtPrice && (\n                <Badge variant=\"sale\" size=\"sm\">\n                  -{Math.round(((product.compareAtPrice - product.price) / product.compareAtPrice) * 100)}%\n                </Badge>\n              )}\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Quick Actions */}\n            <div className=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black/60 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity flex items-center justify-center gap-2\">\n              <Button\n                size=\"sm\"\n                variant=\"primary\"\n                asChild\n              >\n                <Link href={`/${locale}/products/${product.slug}`}>\n                  {locale === 'ar' ? 'ГҸв•ЈГҸв–’ГҸГӮ ГҸВәв”ҳГӨв”ҳГ в”ҳГҘГҸВ¬ГҸВј' : 'View Product'}\n                </Link>\n              </Button>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Content */}\n          <div className=\"p-4\">\n            <h3 className=\"font-semibold mb-2 line-clamp-2 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">\n              {isRTL ? product.nameAr : product.name}\n            </h3>\n            <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n              <PriceDisplay\n                price={product.price}\n                compareAtPrice={product.compareAtPrice}\n              />\n              {product.pointsReward > 0 && (\n                <span className=\"text-xs text-accent-amber\">\n                  +{product.pointsReward} Г”ГңГӯ\n                </span>\n              )}\n            </div>\n            <RatingStars rating={product.rating} count={product.ratingCount} size=\"sm\" />\n          </div>\n        </CardContent>\n      </Card>\n    </Link>\n  );\n}\n","usedDeprecatedRules":[]},{"filePath":"C:\\Users\\USER\\Desktop\\RaadFun\\SSS\\ecom\\src\\app\\[locale]\\platforms\\page.tsx","messages":[{"ruleId":"@typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars","severity":1,"message":"'Music' is defined but never used.","line":3,"column":40,"nodeType":"Identifier","messageId":"unusedVar","endLine":3,"endColumn":45,"suggestions":[{"messageId":"removeUnusedVar","data":{"varName":"Music"},"fix":{"range":[100,107],"text":""},"desc":"Remove unused variable \"Music\"."}]},{"ruleId":"@typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars","severity":1,"message":"'Locale' is defined but never used.","line":7,"column":15,"nodeType":"Identifier","messageId":"unusedVar","endLine":7,"endColumn":21,"suggestions":[{"messageId":"removeUnusedImportDeclaration","data":{"varName":"Locale"},"fix":{"range":[299,341],"text":""},"desc":"Remove unused import declaration."}]}],"suppressedMessages":[],"errorCount":0,"fatalErrorCount":0,"warningCount":2,"fixableErrorCount":0,"fixableWarningCount":0,"source":"import { Metadata } from 'next';\nimport Link from 'next/link';\nimport { ChevronRight, Gamepad2, Film, Music, Smartphone, Cpu, Sparkles } from 'lucide-react';\nimport { Card, CardContent } from '@/components/ui/card';\nimport { Button } from '@/components/ui/button';\nimport { cn } from '@/lib/utils';\nimport type { Locale } from '@/lib/i18n';\n\ninterface PlatformsPageProps {\n  params: Promise<{ locale: string }>;\n}\n\nexport async function generateMetadata({ params }: PlatformsPageProps): Promise<Metadata> {\n  const { locale } = await params;\n  return {\n    title: locale === 'ar' ? 'ГҸВәв”ҳГӨв”ҳГ в”ҳГҘГҸГҒГҸВәГҸВ¬' : 'Platforms',\n    description: locale === 'ar'\n      ? 'ГҸВ¬ГҸГҒв”ҳГјГҸВЎ ГҸВјв”ҳГ в”ҳГЁГҸв•Ј ГҸВәв”ҳГӨв”ҳГ в”ҳГҘГҸГҒГҸВәГҸВ¬ ГҸВәв”ҳГӨв”ҳГ ГҸВ¬ГҸВәГҸВЎГҸВ®'\n      : 'Browse all available platforms',\n  };\n}\n\ninterface PlatformCategory {\n  id: string;\n  name: string;\n  nameAr: string;\n  icon: React.ReactNode;\n  description: string;\n  descriptionAr: string;\n  platforms: Platform[];\n}\n\ninterface Platform {\n  id: string;\n  name: string;\n  nameAr: string;\n  slug: string;\n  icon: string;\n  productCount: number;\n  color: string;\n}\n\nconst PLATFORM_CATEGORIES: PlatformCategory[] = [\n  {\n    id: 'gaming',\n    name: 'Gaming',\n    nameAr: 'ГҸВәв”ҳГӨГҸГәв”ҳГӨГҸв•ЈГҸВәГҸВҝ',\n    icon: <Gamepad2 className=\"w-6 h-6\" />,\n    description: 'Game keys, gift cards, and subscriptions',\n    descriptionAr: 'в”ҳГ в”ҳГјГҸВәГҸВ¬в”ҳГЁГҸВЎ ГҸВәв”ҳГӨГҸГәв”ҳГӨГҸв•ЈГҸВәГҸВҝГҸГ® ГҸВҝГҸГҖГҸВәв”ҳГ©ГҸВәГҸВ¬ ГҸВәв”ҳГӨв”ҳГ§ГҸВ»ГҸВәв”ҳГЁГҸВәГҸГ® в”ҳГӘГҸВәв”ҳГӨГҸВәГҸв”ӨГҸВ¬ГҸв–’ГҸВәв”ҳГўГҸВәГҸВ¬',\n    platforms: [\n      { id: 'steam', name: 'Steam', nameAr: 'ГҸв”ӮГҸВ¬в”ҳГЁв”ҳГ ', slug: 'steam', icon: 'ВӯЖ’Г„В«', productCount: 450, color: 'from-blue-600 to-blue-800' },\n      { id: 'playstation', name: 'PlayStation', nameAr: 'ГҸВҝв”ҳГӨГҸВәв”ҳГЁГҸв”ӮГҸВ¬в”ҳГЁГҸв”Өв”ҳГҘ', slug: 'playstation', icon: 'ВӯЖ’Г„В»', productCount: 320, color: 'from-blue-500 to-indigo-600' },\n      { id: 'xbox', name: 'Xbox', nameAr: 'ГҸГ‘в”ҳГўГҸв”Ӯ ГҸВҝв”ҳГӘв”ҳГўГҸв”Ӯ', slug: 'xbox', icon: 'ВӯЖ’Ж’Гі', productCount: 280, color: 'from-green-500 to-green-700' },\n      { id: 'nintendo', name: 'Nintendo', nameAr: 'в”ҳГҘв”ҳГЁв”ҳГҘГҸВ¬в”ҳГҘГҸВ»в”ҳГӘ', slug: 'nintendo', icon: 'ВӯЖ’Г¶в”Ө', productCount: 150, color: 'from-red-50