nameAr : product.category.name}\n              </div>\n              <h1 className=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-2\">\n                {isRTL ? product.nameAr : product.name}\n              </h1>\n              <RatingStars rating={product.rating} count={product.ratingCount} size=\"md\" />\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Price */}\n            <Card className=\"bg-background-light\">\n              <CardContent className=\"p-6\">\n                <PriceDisplay\n                  price={product.price}\n                  compareAtPrice={product.compareAtPrice}\n                  className=\"text-2xl\"\n                />\n                {product.pointsReward > 0 && (\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-accent-amber mt-2\">\n                    <span className=\"text-lg\">Г”ГңГӯ</span>\n                    <span className=\"font-medium\">\n                      {locale === 'ar'\n                        ? `ГҸВәв”ҳГўГҸв”ӮГҸВҝ ${product.pointsReward} в”ҳГҘв”ҳГ©ГҸГҖГҸВ®`\n                        : `Earn ${product.pointsReward} points`}\n                    </span>\n                  </div>\n                )}\n              </CardContent>\n            </Card>\n\n            {/* Platform Selector */}\n            {product.platforms.length > 1 && (\n              <div>\n                <label className=\"text-sm font-medium mb-2 block\">\n                  {locale === 'ar' ? 'ГҸВәГҸВ«ГҸВ¬ГҸв–’ ГҸВәв”ҳГӨв”ҳГ в”ҳГҘГҸГҒГҸВ®:' : 'Select Platform:'}\n                </label>\n                <div className=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\">\n                  {product.platforms.map((platform) => (\n                    <button\n                      key={platform.id}\n                      className={cn(\n                        'px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border-2 transition-all',\n                        platform.isPrimary\n                          ? 'border-primary bg-primary/20 text-primary'\n                          : 'border-border hover:border-primary/50'\n                      )}\n                    >\n                      {isRTL ? platform.nameAr : platform.name}\n                    </button>\n                  ))}\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            )}\n\n            {/* Actions */}\n            <div className=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3\">\n              <Button size=\"lg\" className=\"flex-1 btn-electric\">\n                <ShoppingCart className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n                {locale === 'ar' ? 'ГҸГәГҸГӮв”ҳГј в”ҳГӨв”ҳГӨГҸв”Ӯв”ҳГӨГҸВ®' : 'Add to Cart'}\n              </Button>\n              <Button size=\"lg\" variant=\"accent\" className=\"flex-1\">\n                {locale === 'ar' ? 'ГҸВәГҸв”ӨГҸВ¬ГҸв–’в”ҳГЁ ГҸВәв”ҳГӨГҸГів”ҳГҘ' : 'Buy Now'}\n              </Button>\n              <Button size=\"lg\" variant=\"outline\">\n                <Heart className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n              </Button>\n              <Button size=\"lg\" variant=\"outline\">\n                <Share2 className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n              </Button>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Delivery Info */}\n            <Card>\n              <CardContent className=\"p-4\">\n                <div className=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n                  <div className=\"text-primary\">{deliveryInfo.icon}</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h4 className=\"font-semibold\">{deliveryInfo.title}</h4>\n                    <p className=\"text-sm text-text-muted\">{deliveryInfo.description}</p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </CardContent>\n            </Card>\n\n            {/* Specifications */}\n            <Card>\n              <CardHeader>\n                <h3 className=\"font-semibold\">\n                  {locale === 'ar' ? 'ГҸВәв”ҳГӨв”ҳГ в”ҳГӘГҸВәГҸГҒв”ҳГјГҸВәГҸВ¬' : 'Specifications'}\n                </h3>\n              </CardHeader>\n              <CardContent>\n                <dl className=\"space-y-2\">\n                  {Object.entries(product.specifications).map(([key, value]) => (\n                    <div key={key} className=\"flex justify-between py-2 border-b border-border/50 last:border-0\">\n                      <dt className=\"text-text-muted\">{key}</dt>\n                      <dd className=\"font-medium\">{value}</dd>\n                    </div>\n                  ))}\n                </dl>\n              </CardContent>\n            </Card>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Description */}\n        <div className=\"mt-12\">\n          <Card>\n            <CardHeader>\n              <h2 className=\"text-xl font-semibold\">\n                {locale === 'ar' ? 'ГҸВәв”ҳГӨв”ҳГӘГҸГҒв”ҳГј' : 'Description'}\n              </h2>\n            </CardHeader>\n            <CardContent>\n              <p className=\"text-text-muted leading-relaxed\">\n                {isRTL ? product.descriptionAr : product.description}\n              </p>\n            </CardContent>\n          </Card>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Reviews Section */}\n        <div className=\"mt-12\">\n          <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-6\">\n            <h2 className=\"text-2xl font-semibold\">\n              {locale === 'ar' ? 'ГҸВәв”ҳГӨГҸВ¬в”ҳГ©в”ҳГЁв”ҳГЁв”ҳГ ГҸВәГҸВ¬ в”ҳГӘГҸВәв”ҳГӨв”ҳГ ГҸв–’ГҸВәГҸВјГҸв•ЈГҸВәГҸВ¬' : 'Reviews'}\n            </h2>\n            <Button variant=\"outline\">\n              <Star className=\"w-4 h-4 mr-2\" />\n              {locale === 'ar' ? 'ГҸГәв”ҳГўГҸВ¬ГҸВҝ ГҸВ¬в”ҳГ©в”ҳГЁв”ҳГЁв”ҳГ ' : 'Write a Review'}\n            </Button>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\n            {/* Rating Summary */}\n            <Card>\n              <CardContent className=\"p-6 text-center\">\n                <div className=\"text-5xl font-bold text-accent-yellow mb-2\">\n                  {product.rating}\n                </div>\n                <RatingStars rating={product.rating} size=\"lg\" />\n                <p className=\"text-sm text-text-muted mt-2\">\n                  {locale === 'ar'\n                    ? `ГҸВҝв”ҳГҘГҸВәГҸГӯв”ҳГҜ ГҸв•Јв”ҳГӨв”ҳГ« ${product.reviewsCount} ГҸВ¬в”ҳГ©в”ҳГЁв”ҳГЁв”ҳГ `\n                    : `Based on ${product.reviewsCount} reviews`}\n                </p>\n              </CardContent>\n            </Card>\n\n            {/* Reviews List */}\n            <div className=\"md:col-span-2 space-y-4\">\n              {[1, 2, 3].map((i) => (\n                <Card key={i}>\n                  <CardContent className=\"p-4\">\n                    <div className=\"flex items-start justify-between mb-2\">\n                      <div>\n                        <div className=\"font-medium\">User {i}</div>\n                        <div className=\"text-xs text-text-muted\">\n                          {locale === 'ar' ? 'в”ҳГ в”ҳГҘГҸв–‘ в”ҳГЁв”ҳГӘв”ҳГ в”ҳГЁв”ҳГҘ' : '2 days ago'}\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                      <RatingStars rating={5 - i * 0.5} size=\"sm\" />\n                    </div>\n                    <p className=\"text-sm text-text-muted\">\n                      {locale === 'ar'\n                        ? 'в”ҳГ в”ҳГҘГҸВ¬ГҸВј ГҸв–’ГҸВәГҸВӘГҸв•Ј! в”ҳГӘГҸГҒв”ҳГӨ ГҸВҝГҸв”ӮГҸв–’ГҸв•ЈГҸВ® в”ҳГӘГҸв•Јв”ҳГ в”ҳГӨ в”ҳГўв”ҳГ ГҸВә в”ҳГ§в”ҳГӘ в”ҳГ ГҸВ¬в”ҳГӘв”ҳГ©ГҸв•Ј.'\n                        : 'Great product! Arrived quickly and worked as expected.'}\n                    </p>\n                  </CardContent>\n                </Card>\n              ))}\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Related Products */}\n        <div className=\"mt-12\">\n          <h2 className=\"text-2xl font-semibold mb-6\">\n            {locale === 'ar' ? 'в”ҳГ в”ҳГҘГҸВ¬ГҸВјГҸВәГҸВ¬ ГҸв–‘ГҸВәГҸВ¬ ГҸГҒв”ҳГӨГҸВ®' : 'Related Products'}\n          </h2>\n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4\">\n            {relatedProducts.map((related) => (\n              <Link key={related.id} href